 (Hazing)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Servitude; Physical Harm; Tracking Devices; Lack of Access to Food<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation from 12\/14\/21 through 12\/14\/22<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>100% participation in chapter education\/bystander intervention education<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Limitations on new member events<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>New member education<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Probation<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of social privileges for Fall 2021<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2021 Description Delta Chi hazed new members through personal servitude, demeaning acts, exercises and degradation. New members were made to engage in acts of personal servitude for active members.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[7],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-691","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-7"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/691","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=691"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/691\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":697,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/691\/revisions\/697"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/w